OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with early outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain soon clearing east. Further rain
OL,7,Fwill spread east from mid-morning,
OL,8,Fthis wintry over the hills. Rain turns
OL,9,Fto showers, the odd bright spell east
OL,10,Flater. These wintry over the hills.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers will continue through
OL,13,Fthe evening but will clear slowly from
OL,14,Fthe south overnight. It will become
OL,15,Fcold as clear spells increase later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
