OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry, early bright spells
OL,6,Feast, otherwise cloudy with rain
OL,7,Fspreading northeast. This heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes and wintry over higher ground.
OL,9,FThe wind strengthens to severe gale in
OL,10,Fwest later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FRain,
OL,13,Fhill snow and severe gales clear
OL,14,Fovernight into Sunday, leaving
OL,15,Ffrequent showers. Mostly dry but
OL,16,Fcloudy Monday and Tuesday with showers
OL,17,Fthen rain spreading east late Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
